familia rodante ( english : rolling family ) is a 2004 comedy drama film , written and directed by pablo trapero , and produced by various countries , including argentina . the film 's executive producers were hugo castro fau and martina gusman , and it was produced by pablo trapero , robert bevan , and donald ranvaud . the picture is about a large argentine family that takes a northern 1000 plus kilometer road trip in an old cramped motor-home to attend a wedding . the family takes part in many adventures along their way to the wedding .